蜱蟎亞綱物種的[[系統發生樹|系統發生樹]]至今仍有爭議，不同文獻為這些物種的分類作過建議。現時最普遍採用的標準是2009年出版的標準教科書《蟎學手冊》（{{lang|en|A Manual of Acarology}}）第三版，把所有蜱蟎物種劃分為三個[[總目|總目]]、六個[[目_(生物)|目]]，分別如下<ref name="Krantz 2009">{{cite book |title=A Manual of Acarology |edition=3rd |editor-first1= Gerald W. |editor-last1= Krantz |editor-first2= D. E. |editor-last2= Walter |year=2009 |publisher= {{tsl|en|Texas Tech University Press||Texas Tech University Press}} |isbn=978-0-89672-620-8}}</ref>：
* '''[[蟎形總目|蟎形總目]]''' '''{{tsl|en|Acariformes}}'''：舊作[[螨形亚目|螨形亚目]]或[[螨形目|螨形目]]，亦作[[真蟎目|真蟎目]]，是整個分類單元多元化程度最高的群組；
** [[恙蟎目|恙蟎目]]（[[Trombidiformes|Trombidiformes]]，舊作[[恙螨亚目|恙螨亚目]]）：plant parasitic mites (spider mites, peacock mites, gall mites, red-legged earth mites, etc.), snout mites, chiggers, hair follicle mites, velvet mites, water mites, etc.
*** [[跳螨亚目|跳螨亚目]] [[Sphaerolichida|Sphaerolichida]]
*** [[前气门亚目|前气门亚目]] [[Prostigmata|Prostigmata]]
** [[疥蟎目|疥蟎目]] ([[Sarcoptiformes|Sarcoptiformes]]，舊作[[疥蟎亞目|疥蟎亞目]]）
*** [[甲蟎亞目|甲蟎亞目]] [[Oribatida|Oribatida]] – oribatid mites, beetle mites, armored mites (also cryptostigmata)
*** [[無氣門類|無氣門類]] [[Astigmata|Astigmata]] – stored product, fur, feather, dust, and human itch mites, etc.
* '''[[盲蛛總目|盲蛛總目]] {{tsl|en|Opilioacariformes}}'''：或作[[盲蛛形總目|盲蛛形總目]]，包括所有外形跟[[盲蛛目|盲蛛目]]（[[Opiliones|Opiliones]]）物種的蟎蟲；
**[[盲蛛目|盲蛛目]]（[[Opilioacarida|Opilioacarida]] <small>Zakhvatkin, 1952</small>，只有[[盲蛛總科|盲蛛總科]]一個總科）；
* '''[[寄蟎總目|寄蟎總目]]''' '''[[Parasitiformes|Parasitiformes]]'''：舊作[[寄螨亚目|寄螨亚目]]或[[寄螨目|寄螨目]]，包括所有蜱類及部分蟎蟲，分為下列三個目<ref name="Zootaxa_Parasitiformes">{{cite book |chapter=Superorder '''Parasitiformes''' <small>Reuter, 1909</small> |chapterurl=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p128.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |authors=FRÉDÉRIC BEAULIEU, ASHLEY P.G. DOWLING, HANS KLOMPEN, GILBERTO J. DE MORAES & DAVID EVANS WALTER |url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |title=Animal biodiversity: An outline of higher-level classification and survey of taxonomic richness |editor=Zhang, Z.-Q. |journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]] |issue=3148 |year=2011 |page=123-128 |publisher=[[Magnolia_Press|Magnolia Press]] |isbn=978-1-86977-850-7 |issn=1175-5334 |language=en |access-date=2016-05-19 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222175509/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；
** {{tsl|en|Holothyrida}} <small>Thon, 1905</small>：只有一個總科；
** [[真蜱目|真蜱目]] [[Ixodida|Ixodida]] <small>Leach, 1815</small>：所有蜱類；
** [[中氣門蟎目|中氣門蟎目]] [[Mesostigmata|Mesostigmata]] <small>G. Canestrini, 1891</small>，又名[[中氣門目|中氣門目]]或[[革蟎目|革蟎目]]，包括所有鳥蟎及植綏蟎；
*** [[单殖板总股|单殖板总股]] [[Monogynaspida|Monogynaspida]]<ref name="ITIS_1117845">{{ITIS |id=1117845 |taxon=Monogynaspida |access-date=2020-04-10 }}</ref>
*** [[三殖板总股|三殖板总股]] [[Trigynaspida|Trigynaspida]]<ref name="ITIS_1117847">{{ITIS |id=1117847 |taxon=Trigynaspida |access-date=2020-04-10 }}</ref>

近二十多年的遺傳學研究使命名規則有不少的變化，然而，有文獻把寄蟎總目下降至目級<ref name="Barker et Murrell 2004">{{cite journal |first1=S.C. |last1=Barker |first2=A. |last2=Murrell |date=2004 |title=Systematics and evolution of ticks with a list of valid genus and species names |journal=Parasitology |volume=129 |issue=7 |pages=S15–S36 |doi=10.1017/S0031182004005207 |name-list-style=amp |pmid=15938503 |url=https://tede.ufrrj.br/jspui/handle/jspui/2545 }}</ref>。其他較近期的研究亦建議蜱蟎亞綱是一個[[多系群|多系群]]，並指蜱類較蟎類其實更接近蜘蛛<ref name="Sanggaard et al 2014">{{cite journal|last1=Sanggaard|first1=Kristian W.|last2=Bechsgaard|first2=Jesper S.|last3=Fang|first3=Xiaodong|title=Spider genomes provide insight into composition and evolution of venom and silk|journal=''[[Nature_Communications|Nature Communications]]'' |issn=2041-1723 |volume=5 |pages=3765 |date=2014-05-06 | doi= 10.1038/ncomms4765|language=en | pmid= 24801114| pmc= 4273655|bibcode=2014NatCo...5.3765S}}</ref>。以下親緣支序圖基於Dabert et al. 2010的分子數據，顯示蟎形總目與屬於蜘蛛的[[避日目|避日目]]（[[Solifugae|Solifugae]]）乃是姊妹分類；反而寄蟎總目跟[[拟蝎目|拟蝎目]]才是姊妹分類<ref name= "DabertWitalinski2010">{{cite journal |last1=Dabert |first1=Miroslawa |last2=Witalinski |first2=Wojciech |last3=Kazmierski |first3=Andrzej |last4=Olszanowski |first4=Ziemowit |last5=Dabert |first5=Jacek |title=Molecular phylogeny of acariform mites (Acari, Arachnida): Strong conflict between phylogenetic signal and long-branch attraction artifacts |journal= Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution|volume=56 |issue=1 |year=2010|pages=222–241 |issn= 1055-7903 |doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2009.12.020|pmid=20060051 }}</ref>。

